      <title>联合信贷银行表示已准备好与法国农业信贷银行就 Banco BPM 进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/unicredit-says-ready-sit-down-with-credit-agricole-over-banco-bpm-2024-12-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit) 的发言人在 LinkedIn 帖子中表示，该银行已准备好与法国农业信贷银行 (Credit Agricole) 谈判，此前法国农业信贷银行增加了其在联合信贷银行的收购目标 Banco BPM 中的潜在持股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/unicredit-says-ready-sit-down-with-credit-agricole-over-banco-bpm-2024-12-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 18:34:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
